WEBVTT

00:01.000 --> 00:10.000
Alex: Hi guys, let's look at the customer feedback.

00:10.000 --> 00:20.000
Sarah: The client is loving the new dashboard view but wants bigger icons.

00:20.000 --> 00:30.000
Alex: Bigger icons? Sure. How long to swap them?

00:30.000 --> 00:40.000
John: Only an hour if I use the SVG library.

00:40.000 --> 00:50.000
Alex: Perfect, John, handle the icons.

00:50.000 --> 01:00.000
Liam: I'll update the style guide to match the new size.

01:00.000 --> 01:10.000
Alex: Thanks Liam. Anything else?

01:10.000 --> 01:20.000
Emma: The search box needs a better placeholder.

01:20.000 --> 01:30.000
Alex: Good point, Emma, take that.

01:30.000 --> 01:40.000
John: We're on track for Friday.

01:40.000 --> 01:50.000
Alex: Great. Nice and easy meeting. See ya!
